# Pulled case dumps may contain customer data — never commit them. Keep dumps
# under .context/ (the recommended `out:` location); the patterns below are a
# backstop for the dump + its .meta.json sidecar written elsewhere.
.context/
*.jsonl.meta.json
*.json.meta.json
*.csv.meta.json
